---
title: Creamy Balsamic Pasta & White Bean Salad  with Mozzarella, Grape Tomatoes & Garlic Toast
description: Bouncy, curly cavatappi pasta stars in this fresh, flavorful pasta salad that’s packed with cannellini beans, cucumber, tomatoes, and mozzarella. A creamy balsamic dressing ties it all together, and crunchy, golden ciabatta toast spread with garlic butter makes a perfect pairing. Best of all, it’s on the table in a speedy 20 minutes!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66d7101007a263836a73ea37-f1292146.jpeg
